            h2 Welcome!
            p.lead This is the next step in the hiring process as QA at EZCORP/Tech Center Guatemala. On this page, you will find a set of exercises related to the quality assurance process inside software development projects. The purpose of these exercises is to evaluate knowledge in quality assurance terms and concepts as well as your skills with documenting, organizing and development of test scenarios.
            p.lead Good luck!
        .row
